consistency /kənˈsɪstənsɪ/

1. N-UNCOUNT Consistency is the quality or condition of being consistent. 连贯性; 一致性 

例： She scores goals with remarkable consistency. 她以非凡的连贯性进球得分。 

2. N-UNCOUNT The consistency of a substance is how thick or smooth it is. 黏稠度 

例： Dilute the paint with water until it is the consistency of milk. 用水把颜料稀释到牛奶的黏稠度。

